A '''wrist laser''' was a type of compact [[Laser/Legends|laser]] weapon capable of inflicting serious damage at extremely close range. Wrist lasers consisted of rechargeable solar-powered [[Gauntlet/Legends|gauntlets]]. A user had the option of causing the chamber of the gauntlet to be overloaded, which would result in a small explosion.

Wrist lasers typically cost 2,000 [[Galactic Credit Standard/Legends|credits]] and 100 credits for a [[Power cell/Legends|power pack]].

Variants of this weapon included the [[LG-5 laser gauntlet]] manufactured by [[Prax Arms/Legends|Prax Arms]], and similarly wrist-mounted [[Wrist blaster/Legends|wrist blaster]].

